      Mike Slater Fills in For Glenn Beck - 8/29/14


Friday, August 29, 2014

 Mike Slater fills in for Glenn today and talks the presidents
    "non-strategy" on ISIS as the UK raises it's threat level to Severe.

  Also, Mike discusses how Glenn inspired him to do what he does and who he is.

           Plus, how to take back America.
